";i:390;s:875:"    					<ul class="namespaces" style="text-align:right;"><li class="namespace_li comments" ><a href="http://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/remarks.php?trope=Main.BearerOfBadNews" >&nbsp;Discussion </a></li> <li class="namespace_li Laconic" style="border-width:2px;margin-right:2px;border-color:silver;"><a href="http://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Laconic/BearerOfBadNews" class="textcolor">&nbsp;Laconic&nbsp;</a> </li> <li class="namespace_li" style="padding-left:4px;"><a href="http://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/relationships.php?t=BearerOfBadNews" title="see/set relationships with other tropes" ><img src="http://static.tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pub/images/family_5772.png" height="16" width="16" style="border:none;"></a></li> <li class="namespace_li Analysis"><a href="http://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Analysis/BearerOfBadNews" class="textcolor">&nbsp;Analysis&nbsp;</a> </li> </ul>
